  "title": "Karma Flower Totem",
  "description": "Changes the totem be a karma flower from hit game Rain World (2017).",
  "body": "<div align=\"center\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/4ad5e7119b4c5cedfd2ac2449b4b9ae9690004a1_0.webp\" alt=\"Karma Flower Totem\" width=\"700\" /> </div>\n\n<div align=\"left\"> \n<p> This Resource Pack replaces the totem texture with a karma flower from Rain World, it also changes the totem pop sound to include a recreation of the saint ascend sound, this means the \"ascension\" sound effect is overlayed on top of the normal totem pop sound. </p>\n</div>\n\n<div align=\"center\"> \n<p> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/1ddf69ba2e01204421fb4575d4361e9121b3fbc6.png\" alt=\"The Karma Flower in the offhand\" width=\"281\"/> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/k6er5ts7/images/50e47a7b6cbbb39fc4b7cf34ed5d5bbab4667047.png\" alt=\"The Karma Flower on the ground\" width=\"500\"/> </p>\n</div>\n\n<div align=\"left\"> \n<p> The flower texture is transparent and can look wierd with some shader packs, otherwise it should work fine. It should also work before 1.21 however I haven't tested it so I'm not sure. </p>\n</div>\n\n<div align=\"center\"> \n<p> If anyone from Videocult or Akupara Games has a problem with this please notify me. </p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<hr>\n\n<div align=\"left\"> \n<p> Check out my resource packs: </p>\n</div>\n\n<div align=\"center\"> \n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/karma-flower-totem\" target=\"_blank\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/66d166ced7b1a62a7eb984756e59dc7e8c148177_0.webp\" alt=\"Karma Flower Totem\" width=\"300\"> </a> \n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/rain-world-mace-sounds\" target=\"_blank\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/fb3aa111f78272dd9c6faea0eff70ccd022f7f2f_0.webp\" alt=\"Ascension Mace Sounds\" width=\"300\"> </a>\n</div>\n\n<hr>\n\n<div align=\"left\">\n<p> Real_Sebastiago on all platforms: </p>\n</div>\n\n<div align=\"center\"> \n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/Real_Sebastiago\" target=\"_blank\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/1f0ab67ef9368ce0c0f9c7eca0a91b28b0b05548.png\" alt=\"My Modrinth\" width=\"150\"> </a>\n<a href=\"https://x.com/Real_Sebastiago\" target=\"_blank\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/fa470473968fd7c1dff5dea35a210826270fb155_0.webp\" alt=\"My Twitter\" width=\"150\"> </a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/Real-Sebastiago\" target=\"_blank\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/31428edc03d18e385f2ac559da825efe43098b95_0.webp\" alt=\"My GitHub\" width=\"150\"> </a>\n</div>",
